---
title: Indian-Inspired Braised Halloumi and Spinach with Roasted Squash and Zesty Rice
description: Inspired by Indian sag paneer, we are swapping the traditional cheese for creamy, golden chunks of halloumi and pairing it up with lots of hearty spinach. Gently spiced with an aromatic blend of spices,  this is a mean, green, veggie-loaded dinner machine!

